f=\"http://touristpass.jp/zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftouristpass.jp%2Fzh-tw&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=16c82b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://touristpass.jp/zh-tw</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">JR東日本</span>Pass<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jreast.co.jp/multi/pass/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jreast.co.jp%2Fmulti%2Fpass%2Findex.html&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=418e0b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jreast.co.jp/multi/pass/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">JR北海道</span>Pass<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/ticket/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jrhokkaido.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fchinese%2Fticket%2Findex.html&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=c170a626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/ticket/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多Pass不能盡錄，詳情請參閱鐵路公司嘅網站<br />\n<br />\n計劃行程，可以參考呢篇「日本鐵路心得」，了解吓基本概念先<br />\n<a href=\"https://simontamhk.com/%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e9%90%b5%e8%b7%af%e5%bf%83%e5%be%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsimontamhk.com%2F%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e9%2590%25b5%25e8%25b7%25af%25e5%25bf%2583%25e5%25be%2597%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=17b0ef40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://simontamhk.com/%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e9%90%b5%e8%b7%af%e5%bf%83%e5%be%97/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">常見問題FAQ：</span></span></strong><br />\n1)（某地方）要點樣去？要搭幾耐先到？<br />\n你去下面乗換案内條link自己查應該快過等人覆你<br />\n<br />\n2) 去（某地方）買唔買pass好？<br />\n請提供詳細行程，等各有經驗嘅巴打可以幫你分析吓同俾啲建議你<br />\n<br />\n3) 成田機場點去／坐咩車入市區好？點買來回先平？<br />\n<a href=\"http://0rz.tw/86tRe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0rz.tw%2F86tRe&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=c6c631c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://0rz.tw/86tRe</a><br />\n<br />\n4) 點樣用JR東日本Eki-net網上劃位?<br />\n<a href=\"http://amm693.wixsite.com/railway\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famm693.wixsite.com%2Frailway&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=93e2c4c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amm693.wixsite.com/railway</a><br />\n（劃位前記得留意攞飛時限、更改或者取消劃位嘅手續費）<br />\n出飛後正常情況範例：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ5v1eJWvWGHkisXXLy8Po2UQ2M1VoZNnzkDt4zB6MDru?filename=rSzsV5a.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSzsV5a.jpg&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=5f3be8f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ5v1eJWvWGHkisXXLy8Po2UQ2M1VoZNnzkDt4zB6MDru?filename=rSzsV5a.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdnE4bve2Deq2MVnz2XXCujjGgQevtKNUf6e4KTpm88yz?filename=2v4D2M0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2v4D2M0.jpg&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=f8d4c5c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdnE4bve2Deq2MVnz2XXCujjGgQevtKNUf6e4KTpm88yz?filename=2v4D2M0.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n5)（某班新幹線）多唔多人搭？會唔會滿座？<br />\n去下面空席案内條link search會準過問我哋<br />\n<br />\n6) 日本連假（例：新年、GW）會唔會好多人搭車？<br />\n會，因為有回鄉潮，自己望下個日曆就自然估到每一日嘅人潮走向，計劃行程嘅時候可以考慮逆向行<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">常用網站：</span></span></strong><br />\n時刻表<br />\n<a href=\"https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/station/time\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransit.yahoo.co.jp%2Fstation%2Ftime&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=d8511658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/station/time</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ekitan.com/timetable/railway\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fekitan.com%2Ftimetable%2Frailway&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=918cfaed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ekitan.com/timetable/railway</a><br />\n<br />\n乗換案内<br />\n<a href=\"https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransit.yahoo.co.jp%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=22e7a2b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n多功能地圖及MAPCODE搜尋器（自駕遊啱用）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mapion.co.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mapion.co.jp%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=c0dac2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mapion.co.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\nJR線（新幹線及在来線特急）空席案内及個別列車運転情報<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jr.cyberstation.ne.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jr.cyberstation.ne.jp%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=229cddd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.jr.cyberstation.ne.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n記錄乘車里程<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noritsubushi.org/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noritsubushi.org%2Findex.php&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=37b8aa5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noritsubushi.org/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n乗車券分割慳錢大法搜尋器<br />\n<a href=\"http://bunkatsu.info/cpg.cgi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbunkatsu.info%2Fcpg.cgi&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=4d4905d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bunkatsu.info/cpg.cgi</a><br />\n<br />\nJR全國Pass使用自助售票機出飛方法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jreast.co.jp/tc/downloads/pdf/mv_operation_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jreast.co.jp%2Ftc%2Fdownloads%2Fpdf%2Fmv_operation_tc.pdf&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=a63de4c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jreast.co.jp/tc/downloads/pdf/mv_operation_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\